The paper presents a novel gripper for autonomous harvesting of strawberries, which involves robotics, computer vision, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves machine learning and control systems, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
